{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey in Ooze Keeper, a tactical roguelike where your wits and strategy are the keys to success. Starting with a single island and a handful of slimes, your task is to cultivate, collect, and manage resources to build a thriving slime farm. Can you balance growth and survival to become the ultimate Ooze Keeper?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2692\ufe0f Strategic Building for Maximum Efficiency</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Starting from a lone island, your task is to revive and expand a once-thriving empire into a bustling slime sanctuary. Place and destroy structures to gather valuable drops and perform specific tasks. Structures are the backbone of your island, providing essential resources and boosting your farm's efficiency. Each structure you build can significantly impact your strategy, making careful planning and placement crucial to your success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144770/extras/screenshot_3.png?t=1735628204\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udfe2 Unleash the Power of Unique Slimes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the heart of &quot;Ooze Keeper&quot;\u2014slimes! These captivating creatures come in a variety of types, each with unique traits and abilities. By breeding different slimes, you can create new, rare varieties, unlocking more ways of generating resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144770/extras/screenshot_5.png?t=1735628204\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144770/extras/screenshot_8.png?t=1735628204\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udcb0 Turn Resources into Wealth</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The resources you gather can be sold for gold coins. Use your earnings to pay the ever-looming rent and invest in further expansions. Your ultimate goal is to amass as much wealth as possible, because failing to pay rent will lead to the downfall of your precious empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfb2 Adapt to Ever-Changing Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every few days, choose between a set of modifiers that can alter the gameplay in significant ways. Choose wisely, as these modifiers bring both opportunities and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144770/extras/screenshot_7.png?t=1735628204\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Apprentice Slime Breeder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3144770/f7b6bfc3c2092d24f40a78ce210764c4dc8c4926.jpg"},{"name":"Journeyman Slime Breeder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3144770/61ee35e845cab82a3a60b33c781f18592dfefff3.jpg"},{"name":"Master Slime Breeder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3144770/e6eabfdc96ce2b7fe64e34ef957b43a4fe30bea9.jpg"},{"name":"Lumberjack Legend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3144770/06dc642b1333503157a20cabb61113109f194bee.jpg"},{"name":"Farming Fanatic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3144770/0abf3e4264f9c5b1a2f4245abd1b736df3ae0d1e.jpg"},{"name":"Mining Maniac","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3144770/3a1d6c803a6dcd6c8ded9fca6630e64f0e2f5ab4.jpg"},{"name":"Bee Keeper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/